{"tid":1200020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想612出一分力或者讀新聞/傳理嘅同我入晒嚟","createTime":"2019-06-10T15:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T20:16:54.000Z","uid":79325,"like":95,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b972789a9f4038b8dc091b30366e8596c005727c","tid":1200020,"uid":79325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"未來記者朋友你地好，大家都知道鏡頭係一個好厲害嘅武器，將來義士們有咩事，都要靠你地嘅鏡頭去洗脫罪名，甚至指控差佬。所以我希望咁多位讀緊傳理嘅巴絲，可以出一分綿力，用你嘅方法去前線記錄差佬嘅所有行為。<br />\n加上，警察係鏡頭面前一定唔敢輕舉妄動，eg唔敢用警棍打頭，更希望有一個監察的作用。<br />\n謝謝大家，念念不忘，必有迴響，用一口氣，點一盞燈，有燈就有人。<br />\n為我地香港未來，下一代未來，靠曬你地未來記者。<br />\nTg: @striveforthetruth<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/USROPLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUSROPLM.jpg&h=e48cc24a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7077aef8dd8b9294ecc26c6646cc5b4f5b17c9d6","tid":1200020,"uid":79325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:53:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"077dfabf83a88ec16e047b960b41c956049d83b7","tid":1200020,"uid":79325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"979c1ed709ae52d5473dd2e6c045cbff7cd28ac8","tid":1200020,"uid":68084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1199409/page/3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1199409/page/3</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以要睇下 個人意見"},{"pid":"ea113a5e9f984bab66d7798e7789f6c6e720601b","tid":1200020,"uid":38364,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:54:03.000Z","msg":"［速投］十一號晚定十二號頭班車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199753</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩入去投個票，再唔出黎就真係太遲啦香港人"},{"pid":"26d46780a6bce43745ef8f741e4f51d97b5ca9aa","tid":1200020,"uid":61257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ag